{"root":{"data":{"id":"d2aertr7hcw0","created":1719451742539,"text":"RiotGame"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af0qawruw0","created":1719452440300,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0ue4rhc0","created":1719452449202,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0v94src0","created":1719452451077,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0w3igvc0","created":1719452452914,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0ws6vd40","created":1719452454406,"text":"赛事","layout_mind_offset":{"x":7.499999980131406,"y":-205.33332834773637}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af130z16w0","created":1719452467998,"text":"html","layout_left_offset":{"x":-9.166666156715792,"y":-14.99999916553503}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af1u1nh8o0","created":1719452526812,"text":".header: 头部区域，包含网站的logo、导航栏和下载链接"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af1xqokjs0","created":1719452534856,"text":".sidebar: 侧边栏，列出各个赛事的链接。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af208tt8w0","created":1719452540307,"text":".content: 内容区域，显示选定赛事的详细信息。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af17c4e200","created":1719452477379,"text":"css","layout_left_offset":{"x":-31.66666490501825,"y":-0.8333332869742662}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af4a438u80","created":1719452718516,"text":"选择器"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af4nha6m00","created":1719452747612,"text":"类选择器（如 .header, .sidebar）：用于选择具有特定类名的元素，并为它们应用样式。\n元素选择器（如 body, div, ul, li）：用于选择特定类型的HTML元素。\n伪类选择器（如 :hover）：用于在用户与元素交互时应用特定的样式。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-181.24999441827356,"y":-19.999999384085413}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af4dp77h40","created":1719452726323,"text":"布局和定位"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af5bio8ds0","created":1719452799939,"text":"Flexbox：在 .header 和 .teams 中使用了Flexbox布局模型，通过 display: flex 和相关属性（如 justify-content, align-items）实现元素的水平和垂直布局。\n绝对定位：通过 position: absolute、top, left 等属性，控制 .content 元素的精确位置。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-299.9999907612806,"y":1.1368683772161603e-13}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af4kcgz4w0","created":1719452740791,"text":"间距和填充："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af5jnjhd40","created":1719452817648,"text":"外边距和内边距：通过 margin 和 padding 属性设置元素之间的间距和内容与边框之间的距离。\n例如，.header .logo 中的 margin-left 和 .header nav ul 中的 margin-right 控制元素之间的水平间距。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-814.9999749014787,"y":38.74999880666519}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af182lzso0","created":1719452478981,"text":"Javascript","layout_left_offset":{"x":-13.333332591586668,"y":10.83333273066421}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af2414nsw0","created":1719452548548,"text":"document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() { ... });:\n 当文档加载完成后执行的事件处理函数，确保在DOM完全加载后再执行JavaScript代码。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-551.2499830238527,"y":38.7499988066653}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af29z9k800","created":1719452561496,"text":"const events = document.querySelectorAll('.sidebar ul li');: 获取侧边栏中所有赛事的列表项。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-524.9999838322406,"y":57.49999822924519}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af2ci87c80","created":1719452566996,"text":"const eventDetails = document.querySelectorAll('.event');: 获取所有赛事详细信息的容器。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-524.9999838322406,"y":57.49999822924519}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af2f4fa4g0","created":1719452572692,"text":"events.forEach(event => { ... });: 遍历每个赛事列表项，并为其添加点击事件监听器。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-524.9999838322406,"y":57.49999822924519}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af2hpu7eg0","created":1719452578340,"text":"点击事件监听器的处理函数通过点击赛事名称，在所有赛事详细信息容器中隐藏非当前赛事的信息，并显示被点击赛事的详细信息。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-524.9999838322406,"y":57.49999822924519}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0xghvfk0","created":1719452455876,"text":"首页"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af6orf0qo0","created":1719452907130,"text":"html"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af7514xvs0","created":1719452942546,"text":"使用 <div> 元素创建不同的区块，如 .header, .image, .game, .image1，用于组织页面内容。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af7abfh6w0","created":1719452954052,"text":"使用 <ul> 和 <li> 创建导航菜单，包含下拉菜单（使用 <ul class=\"dropdown\"> 和嵌套的 <li>）。\n使用 <a> 元素创建链接，将用户引导至其他页面或内部部分。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-624.9999807526679,"y":9.99999969204282}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af6qm2m5c0","created":1719452911160,"text":"css"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af7y5lfaw0","created":1719453005942,"text":"布局"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af8ipxmyw0","created":1719453050708,"text":"使用 Flexbox（display: flex;, justify-content, align-items）实现灵活的布局管理，例如在导航菜单和图片展示区域中。\n通过 position: fixed; 将导航栏固定在页面顶部，确保用户在页面滚动时导航始终可见。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-631.2499805601947,"y":34.9999989221493}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af7yxeaio0","created":1719453007624,"text":"样式"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af8sm3ue00","created":1719453072244,"text":"利用过渡效果（transition）平滑地改变元素的背景颜色和其他属性，增强用户体验。\n使用伪类（:hover）为链接和下拉菜单项添加交互效果，例如改变文本颜色和显示下拉菜单。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-668.7499794053547,"y":38.74999880666542}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af6rjaurs0","created":1719452913170,"text":"JavaScript"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af7iibk680","created":1719452971883,"text":"在 <script> 标签内编写了 JavaScript 代码，通过监听 window 的 scroll 事件来实现滚动效果。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af7j9yroo0","created":1719452973555,"text":"scroll() 函数根据页面滚动的位置动态地添加或移除 .scrolled 类名给 .header 元素，从而改变其样式。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0y4blx40","created":1719452457316,"text":"Valorant","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-8.74999973053741,"y":51.249998421718715}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af9rmozkw0","created":1719453148467,"text":"html"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afa65tza80","created":1719453180099,"text":"头部 (<div class=\"header\">)：包括 Logo、导航菜单和下载链接。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afa8y8z000","created":1719453186171,"text":"主要内容区域 (<div class=\"Hero\"> 和 <div class=\"content\">)：包括英雄展示、内容中心和角色介绍。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afab4raw00","created":1719453190918,"text":"交互元素 (<div class=\"container\">)：包括角色切换按钮和角色介绍的动态展示区域。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af9seljig0","created":1719453150154,"text":"css"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afbaxghog0","created":1719453268841,"text":"盒子模型与布局"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afberx1k80","created":1719453277213,"text":"使用了盒子模型中的 margin 和 padding 属性来控制元素之间的间距和内外边距。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afbic06xk0","created":1719453284958,"text":"display: flex; 和 align-items: center; 等属性用于实现灵活的布局，例如在 .header 中让元素水平排列并垂直居中。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2afbq8ihi80","created":1719453302161,"text":"过渡效果与动画："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afbtitv2g0","created":1719453309315,"text":"使用了过渡效果 (transition)，例如在按钮和图片上定义了过渡属性，使得在状态变化时能够平滑过渡，提升用户体验。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afbw2op4w0","created":1719453314870,"text":"transition-delay 属性用于控制过渡效果的延迟，使不同元素的动画效果可以错开执行。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2afbz5ycls0","created":1719453321598,"text":"动态效果与交互："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afc386o800","created":1719453330440,"text":"使用 JavaScript 结合 CSS 控制了按钮点击后图片和文字内容的切换效果，通过操作 DOM 元素的样式属性实现了动态更新页面内容的功能。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af9ta7gaw0","created":1719453152066,"text":"Javascript"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afahfp1tc0","created":1719453204640,"text":"使用 JavaScript 实现了角色切换的交互功能。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afajolegw0","created":1719453209532,"text":"定义了包含图片路径、角色名称、角色定位和角色简介的数组。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afancds940","created":1719453217501,"text":"使用 showImage() 函数根据按钮点击切换不同的角色信息"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afaohi4q80","created":1719453219987,"text":"控制图片和文字的淡出效果和移动动画，以及淡入新内容的效果，通过操作 CSS 属性实现。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afaswgno80","created":1719453229599,"text":"利用 setTimeout() 函数控制动画的时间和延迟，以确保动画效果流畅。"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0ytlv1c0","created":1719452458845,"text":"商场","layout_mind_offset":{"x":26.249999191612005,"y":161.24999503418826}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afcraaqww0","created":1719453382810,"text":"Javascript"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afec8cbk00","created":1719453506769,"text":"图片轮播功能:"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afeff22yw0","created":1719453513705,"text":"事件绑定与交互"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afei20sc00","created":1719453519447,"text":"定时器控制"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2afcs3yrkg0","created":1719453384604,"text":"css"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afcsy3rio0","created":1719453386426,"text":"html"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afdidogig0","created":1719453441788,"text":"结构定义"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afdpn7sxs0","created":1719453457602,"text":"标签和元素: HTML 使用标签（例如 <div>, <p>, <img> 等）来定义页面上的元素。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afdquqgqg0","created":1719453460233,"text":"文档对象模型（DOM）: HTML 文件被解析成 DOM，DOM 是页面内容的层次化表现，通过 DOM 可以操作和修改页面的内容和结构。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2afdmf1vx40","created":1719453450578,"text":"页面布局"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2afdzx8pk80","created":1719453479976,"text":"局元素: 使用 <div> 和 <span> 等元素进行页面布局和内容分组。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2afe26r0dc0","created":1719453484904,"text":"链接和嵌入资源: <a> 标签用于定义超链接，可以链接到其他页面或资源文件（如图片、音频、视频等）。"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}